)","transliteration":"l-rasūla","root":"رسل","lemmaId":null},{"id":"73:16:4","ayahNum":16,"wordNum":4,"word":"فَأَخَذْنٰهُ","meaning":"and so we seized him (as punishment)","transliteration":"fa-akhadhnāhu","root":"أخذ","lemmaId":null},{"id":"73:16:5","ayahNum":16,"wordNum":5,"word":"أَخْذًا","meaning":"a seizing (object of فَأَخَذْنٰهُ)","transliteration":"akhdhan","root":"أخذ","lemmaId":null},{"id":"73:16:6","ayahNum":16,"wordNum":6,"word":"وَبِيلًا","meaning":"severely/terribly (describing how Pharaoh was seized in فَأَخَذْنٰهُ)","transliteration":"wabīlan","root":"وبل","lemmaId":null},{"id":"73:17:1","ayahNum":17,"wordNum":1,"word":"فَكَيْفَ","meaning":"so how? (connected to كَفَرْتُمْ - you disbelieved)","transliteration":"fakayfa","root":"كيف","lemmaId":3115},{"id":"73:17:2","ayahNum":17,"wordNum":2,"word":"تَتَّقُونَ","meaning":"you (all) protect yourselves","transliteration":"tattaqūna","root":"وقي","lemmaId":null},{"id":"73:17:3","ayahNum":17,"wordNum":3,"word":"إِن","meaning":"if (introduces condition in إِن كَفَرْتُمْ)","transliteration":"in","root":"","lemmaId":502},{"id":"73:17:4","ayahNum":17,"wordNum":4,"word":"كَفَرْتُمْ","meaning":"you (all) disbelieved","transliteration":"kafartum","root":"كفر","lemmaId":3087},{"id":"73:17:5","ayahNum":17,"wordNum":5,"word":"يَوْمًا","meaning":"a day (object of تَتَّقُونَ - you guard against)","transliteration":"yawman","root":"يوم","lemmaId":4512},{"id":"73:17:6","ayahNum":17,"wordNum":6,"word":"يَجْعَلُ","meaning":"he makes/puts/sets (referring to the Day that makes children gray-haired)","transliteration":"yajʿalu","root":"جعل","lemmaId":1223},{"id":"73:17:7","ayahNum":17,"wordNum":7,"word":"ٱلْوِلْدٰنَ","meaning":"the children (subject of يَجْعَلُ - makes/turns)","transliteration":"l-wil'dāna","root":"ولد","lemmaId":null},{"id":"73:17:8","ayahNum":17,"wordNum":8,"word":"شِيبًا","meaning":"gray-haired (describing what the children will be turned into)","transliteration":"shīban","root":"شيب","lemmaId":2187},{"id